Brisbane – Tier 5 (1977 to 2017)

This division is presently known as Capital League 4

 

This listing covers the fifth tier in Brisbane football since 1977:

  • Division 5 – 1977 to 1982
  • Division 4 – 1983
  • Division 3 – 1984 to 1986
  • Division 5 – 1987 to 1996 (except 1995 season, participants unknown)
  • Amateur Division 3 – 1997 to 2001
  • Division 4 – 2002
  • Metro 2 – 2003 to 2012
  • Capital League 4 – 2013 to 2016
